section.p:
In the  administration portal, choose Update configuration settings in the Operation menu. Change the host IP address and port to the ones of the application server to which you deployed the report engine: http://<host IP address>:<port>/birt/frameset?
   __report=${reportname}.rptdesign&SessionId=${sessionid}
   &__locale=${locale}&WSDLURL=${wsdlurl}&SOAPEndPoint=${soapendpoint}
   &wsname=Report&wsport=ReportPort
